s|PC Games]]|issue=41|publisher=[[:de:Computec Media Group|CT Computec Verlag GmbH & Co. KG]]|date=February 1996|pages=124-125|lang=de}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:de:PC Joker|PC Joker]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 87%<ref name=\"PCJokerPCw\">{{cite magazine|last=Magenauer|first=Max|url=https://www.kultboy.com/index.php?site=t&id=11814|title=Twilight \u2014 Games F\u00fcr Individualisten: Worms - Da ist der Wurm drin!|magazine=[[:de:PC Joker|PC Joker]]|issue=37|publisher=Joker-Verlag|date=December 1995|pages=78-79|lang=de}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:de:PC Player|PC Player]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 69/100<ref name=\"PCPlayerPCw\">{{cite magazine|last=Lenhardt|first=Heinrich|url=https://www.kultboy.com/index.php?site=t&id=12228|title=Spiele-test - Worms|magazine=[[:de:PC Player|PC Player]]|issue=36|publisher=[[:de:Future plc|Future Verlag]]|date=December 1995|pages=108-109|lang=de}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[Play (UK magazine)|Play]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 92%<ref name=\"PlayPSw\">{{cite magazine|last=Ahmed|first=Asam|title=Reviews: Worms|magazine=[[Play (UK magazine)|Play]]|issue=1|publisher=[[Paragon Publishing]]|date=November 1995|pages=70-71}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:fr:Player One (magazine)|Player One]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 92%<ref name=\"POSMDw\">{{cite magazine|last=De Steene|first=Julien Van|url=http://download.abandonware.org/magazines/Player%20One/playerone_numero062/Player%20One%20062%20-%20Page%20099%20%281996-03%29.jpg|title=Tests - Megadrive: Worms|magazine=[[:fr:Player One (magazine)|Player One]]|issue=62|publisher=[[:fr:M\u00e9dia Syst\u00e8me \u00c9dition|M\u00e9dia Syst\u00e8me \u00c9dition]]|date=March 1996|page=99|lang=fr}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| 94%<ref name=\"POPSSSw\">{{cite magazine|last=Pottier|first=Christophe|url=ht