ot.com/reviews/worms-review/1900-2531867/|title=Worms Review - Worms is an inexpensive game that offers an exciting strategy competition, a lot of laughs, and fantastic replay value|work=[[GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|date=May 1, 1996|access-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320232038/http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/worms-review/1900-2531867/|archive-date=2014-03-20|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:fr:Gen4|G\u00e9n\u00e9ration 4]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| <small>(DOS)</small> 93%<ref name=\"G4PC1w\">{{cite magazine|last=Ernaux|first=\u00c9ric|url=https://www.abandonware-magazines.org/affiche_mag.php?mag=27&num=473&album=oui|title=Test (PC CD-Rom): Worms - En ver et contre tous|magazine=[[:fr:Gen4|G\u00e9n\u00e9ration 4]]|issue=82|publisher=Computec Media France|date=November 1995|pages=84\u201388|lang=fr}}</ref><br /><small>(Mac)</small> {{Rating|5|5}}<ref name=\"G4PC2w\">{{cite magazine|author=|url=http://download.abandonware.org/magazines/Generation%204/generation4_numero092/Generation%204%20-%20092%20-%20Page%20146.jpg|title=Test Express - Worms (Mac CD-ROM)|magazine=[[:fr:Gen4|G\u00e9n\u00e9ration 4]]|issue=92|publisher=Computec Media France|date=October 1996|page=146|lang=fr}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[IGN]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 8.0/10<ref name=\"IGNPSw\">{{cite web|last=|first=|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/1996/11/26/worms-2|title=Worms is a surprisingly fun strategy game with some quirky additions|work=[[IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff Davis]]|date=November 26, 1996|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[Jeuxvideo.com]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 15/20<ref name=\"Jv.comPCw\">{{cite web|author=eljim|url=http://www.jeuxvideo.com/articles/0001/00013703-worms-test.htm|title=Test de Worms sur PC par jeuxvideo.com|work=[[Jeuxvideo.c